  "prompt": "What does 4 days late on my period mean?",
  "response": "Being 4 days late on your period can have several potential causes, and it\u2019s important to consider your individual circumstances. Here are some common reasons why your period might be late:\n\n### 1. **Pregnancy**\n   - If you\u2019re sexually active, a late period could be a sign of pregnancy. Consider taking a pregnancy test if this is a possibility, especially if you\u2019ve had unprotected sex.\n\n### 2. **Stress**\n   - High levels of stress can disrupt your hormonal balance, potentially delaying ovulation and your period.\n\n### 3. **Hormonal Imbalances**\n   - Conditions like polycystic ovary syndrome (PCOS), thyroid disorders, or other hormonal issues can affect your menstrual cycle.\n\n### 4. **Lifestyle Changes**\n   - Significant changes in weight, diet, exercise, or sleep patterns can impact your cycle.\n\n### 5. **Medications**\n   - Certain medications, such as birth control, antipsychotics, or antidepressants, can alter your menstrual cycle.\n\n### 6. **Perimenopause**\n   - If you\u2019re in your late 30\ns to 40s, irregular periods could be a sign of perimenopause, the transition to menopause.\n\n### 7. **Illness or Infection**\n   - A sudden illness or infection can delay your period.\n\n### What Should You Do?\n- **Take a Pregnancy Test:** If pregnancy is a possibility, take a home pregnancy test. Most tests are accurate even a few days after a missed period.\n- **Track Your Symptoms:** Note any other symptoms, such as cramping, spotting, or mood changes, which could provide additional clues.\n- **Evaluate Stress or Lifestyle Changes:** Reflect on any recent stressors or changes that might be affecting your cycle.\n- **Consult a Healthcare Provider:** If your period is consistently irregular, you\u2019re experiencing unusual symptoms, or you\u2019re concerned, it\u2019s a good idea to see a doctor.\n\nA 4-day delay is not uncommon and may resolve on its own, but staying informed and attentive to your body is always a good idea.",
